data.description: Rare opportunity to have 1.10 acres (5 lots) off of hole #15 on a golf course, in a beautiful & efficient brick home. Walk in to the open floor concept to admire the beautiful fireplace & large kitchen. Stainless steel appliances, tons of cabinet storage, wine fridge, & elongated bar top w/ seating to offer a great space to entertain.  Modern living room, enjoy the long windows allowing tons of natural light and gorgeous views. Large pantry space that walks into a large room to have an office/workout room. Spacious bedroom on the S. boosts 2 large closets. Separate room for storage that leads down the hall from kitchen. Relax in the primary bedroom w/ the natural light surrounding the W. side, leads into large en suite w/ fireplace on the wall & a beautifully tiled shower with a multi spray wall shower system & dual vanity. Huge walkin closet that leads into the laundry room. Walk out to the patio area taking in the serene area & sunsets next to your own fire pit. Community pool, Club house, & golf course via HOA. Located minutes away from Perry Lake & Marina. Roof 3 yrs less.
